OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry, bright morning
OL,6,Fwith some sunshine. Cloud will tend to
OL,7,Fbubble up through the day to give a
OL,8,Ffew heavy afternoon showers between
OL,9,Fsunnier intervals, perhaps with the
OL,10,Fodd rumble of thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will gradually die
OL,13,Fout this evening. Turning cloudier
OL,14,Fthrough the early hours, with rain
OL,15,Fspreading in from the west towards the
OL,16,Fend of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
