OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain, some of which
OL,7,Fmay be on the heavy side. Some drier,
OL,8,Fbrighter periods around the Inverness
OL,9,Farea in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FVariable cloud with showers or a few
OL,13,Fspells of rain, some of which may be
OL,14,Fon the heavy side. Often rather warm
OL,15,Fin any sunny spells around the Moray
OL,16,FFirth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
